{
  "texts": [
    "Sharing a repertoire of capabilities with ChatGPT, Google Bard has demonstrated its efficacy across a spectrum of scientific applications, marking it as a formidable contender in the landscape of advanced AI technologies.",
    "Sulaiman et al.",
    "conducted a study to assess proficiency of Google Bard in critically evaluating DDI screening, and it was subsequently compared with the authorized Lexicomp ® Online ™ database (Sulaiman et al., 2023).",
    "The interrater reliability analysis revealed a minimal concordance between Lexicomp and Google Bard in assessing DDI risk, with a Cohen's kappa (κ) value of 0.01; similarly, a slight agreement between was observed in their severity ratings (κ = 0.02).",
    "However, there was a lack of consensus regarding the reliability rate, reflected by a κ value of -0.02."
  ]
}